(x_n,y_n)
x_n+y_n\sqrt{2}= (1+\sqrt{2})(3+2\sqrt{2})^n.
x_{n+1}+y_{n+1}\sqrt{2}=(x_n+y_n\sqrt{2})(3+2\sqrt{2})
x_{n+1}=3x_n+2y_n,\qquad y_{n+1}=2x_n+3y_n.
